cu.explanation_en: Setting amf_ip_address.ipv4 to a number instead of string will cause type mismatch and AMF connection parsing failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting T1a_cp_dl to [429, 285] (min > max) will cause timing misalignment and front-haul downlink timing failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 T1a_cp_dl 設定為 [429, 285]（最小值 > 最大值）會導致定時錯位並造成前傳下行鏈路定時失敗。
